 "html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Winter in the Cape is no time for outdoor braaiing. &nbsp;Since we don't have an indoor braai, I decided to just braai the chops in the oven. &nbsp;It was absolutely delicious.</p>\n\n\n<div data-recipe-slot=\"1\"></div>\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;\" href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-0711.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1679\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-0711-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 071\"></a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-064.jpg\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-064-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 064\" class=\"wp-image-1678\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-085.jpg\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-3-085-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 3 085\" class=\"wp-image-1675\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"></p>",
